          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Comprehensive SERP research — see everything the top 20 competitors cover</h4><p>Writers know exactly what to include before they start. The brief almost writes itself from Frase's competitive analysis.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Section-by-section AI generation that follows the research brief</h4><p>Generates content that covers what competitors cover. Less random than ChatGPT, more structured than Jasper.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Featured snippet targeting for People Also Ask positions</h4><p>Identifies questions from Google's PAA box and formats content to capture those answer positions.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest limitation: Solo plan too limited (4 briefs/month); big price jump to Basic ($45/mo)</h4><p>The pricing structure is awkward for small businesses that need more than 4 briefs but don't want to pay $45/mo for 30.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px;"><strong>Pricing:</strong> Solo $15/mo (4 briefs) · Basic $45/mo (30 briefs) · Team $115/mo (unlimited, 3 users) · $1 trial</p>
