        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Koala generates complete articles — title, outline, headers, body, meta description, and FAQ — from a single keyword in 2-3 minutes. At $9/mo for 15 articles, it's the cheapest effective output tool in the field. WordPress integration allows direct publishing. The catch: content requires editorial review before publishing. It's not publish-and-forget — it's generate-review-publish. But the time investment is still significantly lower than writing from scratch.</p>
